{
  "id": "adv_event_2307_01_05_01",
  "title": "結局\nいつも通り",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いくらなんでも、こんなやり方はないでしょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is just ridiculous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.5666666666999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "三番勝負で負けたままで終われないからって\nいきなりライブバトルをねじ込んでくるなんて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As they can't stand losing the three challenges‚\nthey suddenly throw in a live battle!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7634469669,
      "endTime": 9.2717914265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.4643993696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "よっしゃ！　この番組の実況がトレンド一位！！\nいや～、あいつらの往生際が悪くて良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! This show's trending number one!!\nOh man‚ I'm glad they didn't know when to give up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4643993696,
      "endTime": 18.1384580931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaの注目度を上げるための\n貴い犠牲になってくれてありがとう～って感じ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to them‚\nkana is getting all this attention!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3977335931,
      "endTime": 24.831066799200002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0310669264
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "まさしく、『策士策に溺れる』といったところですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Truly‚ \"A strategist drowns in their own schemes.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0310669264,
      "endTime": 29.6218832335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "プロデューサーと共謀して、三番勝負の種目は弄れても\nVENUSプログラムのAIは操作出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They can conspire with the producer to rig the challenges‚\nbut they can't manipulate the VENUS Program AI.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.8310669264,
      "endTime": 36.9065996489,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0977335931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "あーあ、可哀想なやつら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aw‚ poor things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0977335931,
      "endTime": 40.5796157361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "せめてルール通りにやってれば\nたとえ惨めに負けても、プライドだけは守れたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they'd just followed the rules‚\nthey could've at least kept their pride‚ even if they lost miserably.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7722236794,
      "endTime": 47.456532017600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6491399608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトルはまだこれからですよ\n……でも三人とも、負けるつもりは毛頭なさそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live battle is still ahead of us.\n…But it seems none of you are planning to lose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6491399608,
      "endTime": 55.9716571652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "当然",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1642651084,
      "endTime": 57.8409063223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0335142656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "何か、気になることでもありました？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.0335142656,
      "endTime": 60.583514265599995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや……みなさん、一致団結していらっしゃるなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I just see how united you all are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7761222088,
      "endTime": 64.99278895489999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.7761222088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "縁起でもないこと言わないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't curse us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1853968982,
      "endTime": 67.5142176513,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.7187302315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "あ～、{user}ってば可哀想に\n仕事がキツ過ぎて、幻影見えちゃってるよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aw‚ poor {user}.\nThe work's so tough you're seeing things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7187302315,
      "endTime": 75.08539683459999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（仕事が大変なのは、あなた方のせいもあるんですが）\n（……とは、言わないでおこう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The hard work is partly because of you all‚ but…）\n（…I'll keep that to myself…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2853968982,
      "endTime": 81.2364398365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4290477797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "あいつらに、格の違いってものを見せてあげるわ\n……ⅢX、行くわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll show them the difference in our level.\n…ⅢX‚ let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4290477797,
      "endTime": 90.1146717117,
      "sfxList": []
    },
